{"tid":221441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整污糟左本護照，洗唔洗換","createTime":"2017-04-28T16:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T02:46:10.000Z","uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"afd17d0a89eb5ff73266e8ad12f7fd796b677e99","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"我本火車頭整污糟左，成本個角有個綠色跡， 膠果版無事。 但個皮入面層紙有四分一比個綠色跡cover 左。 洗唔洗換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ad205418d65ba126f239bf819df9b5384cba40","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"推，我已經book 左聽日入境處，但我家姐又話唔洗換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 究竟換唔換好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfe972cfdf322d60c5ed961cc6e65b2edc3161c","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"真係無人整污糟左護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇咁勁呀你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43d1ba07782874fcff2978aa8fe6a0f82f45520","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"109dfb8ab3bff2025595456e7b2a709496622b06","tid":221441,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:31:07.000Z","msg":"要 當損毀"},{"pid":"ee683b3023ca482855e4355ed024679486ae1c0e","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要 當損毀</blockquote><br />\n但學術台有人話晶片無事既話唔洗換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最多比人問下，<br />\n如果真係問，但我又唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為我都唔知會整污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cdbb2b98b0d9fbbee3ece51cdcd192654f77d2","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b7cee15034082629cc64ffe6332b8e69ffb85f4","tid":221441,"uid":29523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要 當損毀</blockquote><br />\n但學術台有人話晶片無事既話唔洗換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最多比人問下，<br />\n如果真係問，但我又唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為我都唔知會整污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，<br />\n<br />\n學術角度黎講係唔洗換，只不過睇過關條友心情，輸撚左馬咪唔放你，要你換囉，就係咁撚簡單。<br />\n<br />\n宜家連登做埋入境處咩？乜柒都拎上黎問，答撚完又唔撚信。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61667710b81cdbafe2b7bff9a55cc0031e3a6290","tid":221441,"uid":34865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"香港用無咩大問題，出國就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83f715213d7404923a49b0153415f133fd1600e","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"我而家搞緊，佢地用左三條友幫我搞，好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3880a4fdb1e62fc77f2a6142f1c1660d6d571db","tid":221441,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我而家搞緊，佢地用左三條友幫我搞，好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚捉你去暗角咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91907c223b93cf1d81a07f10892e299190ff67f3","tid":221441,"uid":47529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"之前唔小心漏左本護照落洗衣機洗<br />\n之後都用到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7691d23c29e0baf66d02d3f2b7f9b5c9a18f0a22","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我而家搞緊，佢地用左三條友幫我搞，好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚捉你去暗角咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\naco 交比 一粒花 一粒花又話唔識搞，要交比房入面果個。 跟手坐一粒花後面果個兩粒花，又企左起身望住我。 我未見過大蛇屙屎， 有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班友又話下次再整污糟就扣我年期，姐係係下次再整污糟，無得換新既十年期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要用返原本果個期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1612fa65e452fb609065656bce8788e9803863a","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前唔小心漏左本護照落洗衣機洗<br />\n之後都用到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\naco 見到我本護照，佢話唔係損壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我話唔係壞我就唔搞喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住佢話，唔係壞，但一定用唔到，要填第二份form , 仲要比主任加簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2534eff4e988cee0e13e3c6eaf44436dccf57d1","tid":221441,"uid":6290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:20:12.000Z","msg":"咁你不如直接報失換個本啦<br />\n搞咁多野做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556ed70c3d3114c13138d82385bb6e2f75653267","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你不如直接報失換個本啦<br />\n搞咁多野做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無諗過呢樣野，我原本係諗住攞本比佢睇下仲用唔用到，用到我就唔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283d395cc147b1f667c0c49ca3d75155ba89d6d0","tid":221441,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:34:12.000Z","msg":"你而家唔換<br />\n到時去到機場畀班地勤閘住唔畀boarding pass你嗰陣唔好返嚟呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88cf4319191de25702b15dd3ad17e49118c994e","tid":221441,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你而家唔換<br />\n到時去到機場畀班地勤閘住唔畀boarding pass你嗰陣唔好返嚟呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換左喇"}]}